        const article = `%7B%22lang%22%3A%22en-US%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22Tiantianlu%20Cup%22%2C%22html%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22kecare%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ETian%20Tian%20Lu%20Cup%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20id%3D%5C%22sponsors%5C%22%3ESponsors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20sponsorship%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kecare.me%5C%22%3EKecare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20best%20static%20site%20generation%20framework%20in%20the%20world%2C%20meow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20sponsorship%20of%20the%20world%26%2339%3Bs%20best%20Ts%20full-stack%20framework%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.milkio.fun%5C%22%3Emilkio%3C%2Fa%3E%20meow%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you%20for%20the%20sponsorship%20of%20the%20world%26%2339%3Bs%20best%20personal%20development%20award%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fioralune.com%5C%22%3EFioralune%20Awards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meow~%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20other%20sponsors%20accepted%20meow!!!!!!!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20id%3D%5C%22about-this-event%5C%22%3EAbout%20This%20Event%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tournament%20was%20inspired%20by%20seeing%20a%20series%20of%20bizarre%20experiences%20from%20Xpl%2C%20and%20we%20felt%20that%20grassroots%20CS%20could%20also%20have%20better%20tournaments.%20So%20the%20Tian%20Tian%20Lu%20Cup%20was%20born.%20This%20Tian%20Tian%20Lu%20Cup%20was%20fully%20funded%20by%20me%20personally.%20It%20is%20a%20single-elimination%20tournament%20where%208%20teams%20compete%20in%20all%20matches%20as%20Bo3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20id%3D%5C%22time-schedule%5C%22%3ETime%20Schedule%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20tournament%20has%20been%20held%2C%20it%26%2339%3Bs%20mainly%20for%20fun.%20Friendship%20first%2C%20competition%20second%2C%20meow.%20If%20you%26%2339%3Bre%20purely%20after%20competitive%20gameplay%2C%20you%20don%26%2339%3Bt%20need%20to%20join%20our%20Tian%20Tian%20Lu%20Cup%20meow%E2%80%94we%26%2339%3Bre%20here%20for%20fun%2C%20meow.%20The%20registration%20rank%20limit%20is%20from%20C%2B%20to%20defense%20S%20meow.%20No%20higher%20ranks%2C%20meow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20idea%20is%20that%20after%20players%20sign%20up%2C%20the%20event%20organizers%20will%20divide%20them%20into%20balanced%20groups%20based%20on%20their%20skill%20levels.%20The%20players%20will%20then%20have%20a%20week%20of%20preparation%20time%20(bushi)%2C%20followed%20by%20a%203-day%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20the%20registration%20deadline%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20will%20registration%20start%3F%2040%20people%20(8%20teams)%20is%20the%20direct%20cutoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20days%20after%20the%20registration%20deadline%2C%20the%20event%20team%20will%20divide%20the%20groups.%20Members%20can%20choose%20a%20captain%20and%20a%20team%20name%20on%20their%20own.%20The%20captain%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20map%20selection%20and%20ban%2Fpick%20(BP)%20in%20the%20subsequent%20Bo3%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20the%20start%20time%20of%20the%20match%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20plan%20was%20to%20hold%20the%20first%20round%20of%20the%20quarterfinals%20(8%20advancing%20to%204)%20on%20July%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20round%20of%20the%20semi-finals%20(4%20into%202)%20will%20be%20held%20on%20July%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third-place%20match%20and%20final%20will%20be%20held%20on%20July%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20lasts%20three%20days%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20id%3D%5C%22tournament-prize-money%5C%22%3ETournament%20Prize%20Money%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20thank%20a%20certain%20group%20friend%20for%20sponsoring%205%20pieces%20of%20M%26amp%3BG%20erasers%20to%20be%20distributed%20to%20the%205%20champions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20certain%20group%20friend%20for%20sponsoring%20one%20piece%20of%20M%26amp%3BG%20eraser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20it%20was%20entirely%20funded%20by%20me%20personally%2C%20I%20don%26%2339%3Bt%20have%20much%20money%20meow.%20So%20the%20competition%20is%20mainly%20for%20entertainment%2C%20don%26%2339%3Bt%20come%20to%20stomp%20on%20weaker%20players%20for%20a%20few%20dollars%20and%20affect%20meow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChampion%3A%20250%20RMB%20%2B%205%20pieces%20of%20M%26amp%3BG%20erasers%20(One%20KFC%20meal%20per%20person%2C%20meow)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunner-up%20150%20RMB%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%20place%2050%20RMB%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20rest%2C%20I%20will%20personally%20bear%20the%20cost%20of%20one%20M%26amp%3BG%20eraser%20per%20person.%20Alright%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20id%3D%5C%22will-there-be-live-streaming-or-commentary-meow%5C%22%3EWill%20there%20be%20live%20streaming%20or%20commentary%2C%20meow%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20a%20livestream%2C%20exclusive%20on%20Bilibili%20meow.%20But%20there%20might%20not%20be%20commentary%20meow%2C%20because%20I%20can%26%2339%3Bt%20afford%20it%20meow%2C%20I%20don%26%2339%3Bt%20have%20money%20meow.%20I%26%2339%3Bll%20try%20to%20contact%20some%20Bilibili%20uploaders%20to%20see%20if%20they%20can%20provide%20commentary%20meow.%20I%20don%26%2339%3Bt%20have%20money%20meow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20id%3D%5C%22volunteer%5C%22%3EVolunteer%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%26%2339%3Bt%20have%20money%20meow%2C%20so%20I%20might%20need%20volunteers%20working%20for%20love%20to%20help%20with%20promotion%2Fediting%2Fevent%20planning%2Forganizing%20and%20other%20activities%20meow.%20If%20you%26%2339%3Bre%20interested%20and%20enthusiastic%2C%20welcome%20welcome%20meow.%20We%26%2339%3Bll%20be%20good%20friends%20meow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20id%3D%5C%22sponsorship%5C%22%3ESponsorship%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20not%20accept%20sponsorship%20from%20any%20individuals%20or%20organizations%2C%20meow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taste%20changes%20once%20money%20is%20involved%2C%20meow.%20No%20sponsorships%20are%20accepted%20at%20present%2C%20meow.%20Since%20it%20is%20funded%20by%20myself%2C%20the%20final%20interpretation%20right%20belongs%20t