lly.%20It%20is%20a%20single-elimination%20tournament%20where%208%20teams%20compete%20in%20all%20matches%20as%20Bo3.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Time%20Schedule%5Cn%5CnBecause%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20tournament%20has%20been%20held%2C%20it's%20mainly%20for%20fun.%20Friendship%20first%2C%20competition%20second%2C%20meow.%20If%20you're%20purely%20after%20competitive%20gameplay%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20join%20our%20Tian%20Tian%20Lu%20Cup%20meow%E2%80%94we're%20here%20for%20fun%2C%20meow.%20The%20registration%20rank%20limit%20is%20from%20C%2B%20to%20defense%20S%20meow.%20No%20higher%20ranks%2C%20meow.%5Cn%5CnOur%20idea%20is%20that%20after%20players%20sign%20up%2C%20the%20event%20organizers%20will%20divide%20them%20into%20balanced%20groups%20based%20on%20their%20skill%20levels.%20The%20players%20will%20then%20have%20a%20week%20of%20preparation%20time%20(bushi)%2C%20followed%20by%20a%203-day%20tournament.%5Cn%5CnWhat%20is%20the%20registration%20deadline%3F%5Cn%5CnWhen%20will%20registration%20start%3F%2040%20people%20(8%20teams)%20is%20the%20direct%20cutoff.%5Cn%5CnWithin%20two%20days%20after%20the%20registration%20deadline%2C%20the%20event%20team%20will%20divide%20the%20groups.%20Members%20can%20choose%20a%20captain%20and%20a%20team%20name%20on%20their%20own.%20The%20captain%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20map%20selection%20and%20ban%2Fpick%20(BP)%20in%20the%20subsequent%20Bo3%20matches.%5Cn%5CnWhat%20is%20the%20start%20time%20of%20the%20match%3F%5Cn%5CnThe%20original%20plan%20was%20to%20hold%20the%20first%20round%20of%20the%20quarterfinals%20(8%20advancing%20to%204)%20on%20July%2020.%5Cn%5CnThe%20second%20round%20of%20the%20semi-finals%20(4%20into%202)%20will%20be%20held%20on%20July%2021.%5Cn%5CnThe%20third-place%20match%20and%20final%20will%20be%20held%20on%20July%2022.%5Cn%5CnIt%20lasts%20three%20days%20in%20total.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Tournament%20Prize%20Money%3F%5Cn%5CnFirst%20of%20all%2C%20thank%20a%20certain%20group%20friend%20for%20sponsoring%205%20pieces%20of%20M%26G%20erasers%20to%20be%20distributed%20to%20the%205%20champions.%5Cn%5CnSecondly%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20certain%20group%20friend%20for%20sponsoring%20one%20piece%20of%20M%26G%20eraser.%5Cn%5CnBecause%20it%20was%20entirely%20funded%20by%20me%20personally%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20much%20money%20meow.%20So%20the%20competition%20is%20mainly%20for%20entertainment%2C%20don't%20come%20to%20stomp%20on%20weaker%20players%20for%20a%20few%20dollars%20and%20affect%20meow.%5Cn%5CnChampion%3A%20250%20RMB%20%2B%205%20pieces%20of%20M%26G%20erasers%20(One%20KFC%20meal%20per%20person%2C%20meow)%5Cn%5CnRunner-up%20150%20RMB%5Cn%5CnThird%20place%2050%20RMB%5Cn%5CnFor%20the%20rest%2C%20I%20will%20personally%20bear%20the%20cost%20of%20one%20M%26G%20eraser%20per%20person.%20Alright%2C%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Will%20there%20be%20live%20streaming%20or%20commentary%2C%20meow%3F%5Cn%5CnThere%20will%20be%20a%20livestream%2C%20exclusive%20on%20Bilibili%20meow.%20But%20there%20might%20not%20be%20commentary%20meow%2C%20because%20I%20can't%20afford%20it%20meow%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20money%20meow.%20I'll%20try%20to%20contact%20some%20Bilibili%20uploaders%20to%20see%20if%20they%20can%20provide%20commentary%20meow.%20I%20don't%20have%20money%20meow.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Volunteer%3F%5Cn%5CnI%20don't%20have%20money%20meow%2C%20so%20I%20might%20need%20volunteers%20working%20for%20love%20to%20help%20with%20promotion%2Fediting%2Fevent%20planning%2Forganizing%20and%20other%20activities%20meow.%20If%20you're%20interested%20and%20enthusiastic%2C%20welcome%20welcome%20meow.%20We'll%20be%20good%20friends%20meow.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Sponsorship%3F%5Cn%5CnWe%20do%20not%20accept%20sponsorship%20from%20any%20individuals%20or%20organizations%2C%20meow.%5Cn%5CnThe%20taste%20changes%20once%20money%20is%20involved%2C%20meow.%20No%20sponsorships%20are%20accepted%20at%20present%2C%20meow.%20Since%20it%20is%20funded%20by%20myself%2C%20the%20final%20interpretation%20right%20belongs%20to%20me%2C%20meow.%20This%20is%20a%20recreational%20competition%2C%20meow.%20If%20you%20cause%20trouble%2C%20get%20out%2C%20meow.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Follow-up%3F%5Cn%5CnIf%20this%20event%20goes%20smoothly%20and%20receives%20good%20feedback%2C%20then%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20hold%20the%20Tian%20Tian%20Lu%20Cup%20S2%20in%20mid-August%20meow%2C%20which%20is%20also%20funded%20by%20me%20meow%2C%20and%20it's%20an%20entertainment%20competition%20meow.%5Cn%5CnLater%2C%20you%20can%20vote%20to%20choose%20the%20game%20content%2C%20meow.%20Anything%20for%20fun%20is%20fine%2C%20meow.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Professional%20Development%3F%5Cn%5CnI%20won't%20meow%2C%20because%20I%20have%20no%20money%20meow%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20time%20meow%2C%20I%20need%20to%20work.%20It%20will%20always%20be%20just%20a%20fun%20competition.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20How%20to%20join%20us%20meow%5Cn%5Cn!%5Bimage-20260704093444493%5D(%2Fassets%2Ftiantianlubei.png)%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20Thanks%20again%5Cn%5CnThank%20you%20to%20the%20best%20static%20site%20generation%20framework%20in%20the%20world%20%5BKecare%5D(kecare.me)%20for%20sponsoring%20meow.%5Cn%5CnThanks%20for%20the%20sponsorship%20from%20the%20best%20TS%20full-stack%20framework%20%5Bmilkio%5D(milkio.fun)%20meow%5Cn%5CnThank%20you%20for%20the%20sponsorship%20of%20the%20%5BFioralune%20Awards%5D(fioralune.com)%2C%20which%20will%20be%20the%20best%20personal%20development%20award%20in%20the%20world%2C%20meow.%5Cn%5CnIf%20you%20are%20interested%20in%20or%20have%20knowledge%20of%20programming%2C%20and%20are%20interested%20in%20participating%20in%20the%20development%20of%20my%20Kecare%20framework%2C%20then%20you%20are%20welcome.%5Cn%5Cn!%5Bimage-20260704093552371%5D(%2Fassets%2Fkecaregroups.png)%22%7D`
